e administrative action brought against Goldman. In the Offer, Goldman agreed to submit complete applications for registration and to respond promptly to requests for additional information; an administrative fine of $2,500, and to comply with specified undertakings and representations. On that same date, the RICE Section received a signed Undertakings and Representations and Consent to Entry of Order. Consent Orders for each of these documents were issued and filed on May 24, 2016.",
